Product Manager.job_description:
Job Description
Coordinate with Business teams, participant community & others to define FRS for different apps, other technology components, etc.;
Coordinate with external agencies for testing & certification of apps;
Create, maintain & monitor product milestone & timeline plans for different apps & technology components;
Job Requirement
At least 4-6 years of hands-on product management experience, with proven expertise in business requirements gathering & analysis;
 Excellent understanding of developing product milestone & timeline plans;
Excellent experience in developing use-case stories, technical requirement specifications (SRS/ SDD), functional requirement specifications (FRS) and Non-Functional requirement specifications (including security, availability and performance criteria);
Excellent understanding of Agile-based project delivery, project management & issue tracking tools such as Github / Jira;
SALARY
₹1200000 - ₹2500000 PA.
JOB LOCATION
Bengaluru
JOB TYPE
Full Time Permanent

